
Basic Commands

cd
Change directory

mkdir
Make directory

mv
Move (use to rename also, e.g. mv name1 name2)

rmdir
Remove directory (must be empty)

sudo
Run with admin privs

top
list of processes, memory, etc



Debian-specific (Ubuntu)

apt-get install <package>
Installs specific package (needs sudo)

apt-get update
Updates package list with most recent officially supported version (needs sudo)

apt-get upgrade
Upgrades packages (requires sudo)


